description:
Jayogen is a Rookie this year. She's only done one match at US and that was the Tag finale that she wrestled for 1 round. She impressed us in that one round. Today she's going up against her tag partner, Bella Rossi. Bella has years of experience. She has been impressive in her tournament matches. She narrowly lost the Penny Barber Last season in the Welter Weight tournament. She's here today to show the world she's ready to kick ass and take virginity. If she win's she gets to take Jayogen's on cam virginity. No one has ever fucked Jayogen on cam.....could today be our lucky day?
This match was shot and Streamed LIVE on October 18th. Dont miss the next Live show November 15th. The winner of this match takes on Penny Barber!
title: Amazing Welterweight match up. 4 pt difference!
